divs: Sighting Details I looked up to the sky like I always do and noticed a dark object gliding across not at all like a plane.Too slow for a plane, no lights or sound. As it got closer I yelled for my daughter to bring her phone so we could maybe get a picture. Well of all times for her phone to be dead. We kept watching it float across the sky and not in a straight line. The lower it got we could see it had pointed shapes sticking out. Longer points were in the back. WE watched it in awe when all of a sudden it vanished before our eyes.. We asked each other where had it gone??? I am glad my daughter got to see this with me. I will keep watching the sky like I always do because I know it will return.
Summary: I looked up to the sky and saw a dark object gliding getting closer. It was too high to be a bird and had no flashing lights like a plane.
